{
  "stem": "8370.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was publicized all around the world after war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Second, which I was a little bit involved, was helping the people to escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, what was the procedure?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If somebody tried to escape, it was impossible to escape direct from the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the camp was surrounded with barbed wire under power, electricity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Plus, you had, on the towers, you had machine guns and guards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during the day, the guards surrounded outside-- not the camp concrete one or two, three, fields of the camp, but all around the area where we worked, all around.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only by night, they come on the towers surrounding different camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by day, they have been ready.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a question to hide yourself somewhere outside the main camp for three days, because when they find out that somebody escaped, for three days they called this the [? grosse ?] [? postkarten. ?] The big chain of guards was far away from the camp, waiting for the prisoner who escaped, that he will try to pass.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After three days, nobody passed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they moved at night, the guards, close to the camp, direct to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this prisoner, who already was in hiding outside, was already outside the chain of the guards.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was much easier to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was question to supply them in advance, in this place where they were-- they're supposed to be in hiding-- with food and water for three days.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was not my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My job was to take a prisoner who intended to escape, or who was, I would say, was lucky to receive the right to escape.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because not everybody, maybe if they-- not everybody could.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
